s-expand">上知乎日报了，纪念一下！ 必须用视频展示，欢迎来到《舒克日记》版的飞行技术大全。一、牛逼的动能管理1、什么叫五边？什么叫下降率？我不知道。我只知道两点之间最近距离就是我。2、乘客：啊撞山啦啊撞山啦啊撞山啦啊撞山啦。我：嚷嚷什么，谁跟我撞衫了…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/268608943/answer/339611259">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="1591"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/wei-cheng-hao-80" data-hovercard='p$t$wei-cheng-hao-80'>魏承澔</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/zheng-yi-jie-98" data-hovercard='p$t$zheng-yi-jie-98'>aaoeao</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/will-95-77" data-hovercard='p$t$will-95-77'>Eddie</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>上知乎日报了，纪念一下！</p><p><br></p><p>必须用视频展示，欢迎来到《舒克日记》版的飞行技术大全。</p><hr><p>一、牛逼的动能管理</p><p>1、什么叫五边？什么叫下降率？我不知道。我只知道两点之间最近距离就是我。</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956472495583354880" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-42c04de4a8f8a8fc4a6be5206701d440_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956472495583354880">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-42c04de4a8f8a8fc4a6be5206701d440_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956472495583354880</span>              </span>            </a><p>2、乘客：啊撞山啦啊撞山啦啊撞山啦啊撞山啦。我：嚷嚷什么，谁跟我撞衫了？</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956479419028664320" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-056127fd315a1cde199afd859063c23b_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956479419028664320">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-056127fd315a1cde199afd859063c23b_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956479419028664320</span>              </span>            </a><p>3、乘客：师傅，看不出来咱这还是水上飞机呢？我：不是。乘客：……那你往河上飞？！</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956481821861457920" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c494e4663b802f5a56bec8074ab27577_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956481821861457920">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c494e4663b802f5a56bec8074ab27577_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956481821861457920</span>              </span>            </a><p>4、乘客：师傅，我咋眼花了感觉这跑道不是直线呢？我：你没眼花，这跑道就是歪的，习惯就好。</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956482788170469376" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-fcef15abb9b82edb22a67afeb59fd435_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956482788170469376">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-fcef15abb9b82edb22a67afeb59fd435_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956482788170469376</span>              </span>            </a><p>5、加勒比海最有趣的两条跑道St. Barts和Saba</p><p>St. Barts</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956484345591066624" target="_blank" data-video-id