871983616</span>              </span>            </a><p>2、杜塞尔多夫，一个只有侧风的地方。</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956487299538620416" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d4662460c99ee81a5a5449f1a930121d_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956487299538620416">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d4662460c99ee81a5a5449f1a930121d_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956487299538620416</span>              </span>            </a><p>3、红牛比赛，飞行员在距离地面只有几米的地方加速失速（Accelerated Stall），之后成功改出。</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956487931045699584" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-46874572d6448648aa4a490bd5336ac6_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956487931045699584">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-46874572d6448648aa4a490bd5336ac6_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956487931045699584</span>              </span>            </a><p>4、军用直升机飞行员，尝试在颠簸的船上降落军机</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956488376610750464" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a6cad5b9eb150b0ac31d2d9ae302b8ca_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956488376610750464">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a6cad5b9eb150b0ac31d2d9ae302b8ca_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956488376610750464</span>              </span>            </a><hr><p>其实还有，否则怎么叫百科呢，不过知乎只允许一个回答当中传10个视频，而每个问题只有一个回答。</p><p>更多的视频，敬请关注专栏《舒克日记》。<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/aviator" class="internal">舒克日记</a></p></script><a class="time" href="/question/268608943/answer/339611259">2018-03-12</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>1591</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="21877083"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">177 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9ea42ca73f6a352ecd5cf4ea79029848_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-share">分享</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-collect">收藏</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-thank ">感谢</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-report">举报</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9ea42ca73f6a352ecd5cf4ea79029848_m.jpg"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></div></div></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-92105503"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/268608902/answer/341241386"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="21877066"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="268608902"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="92105503"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="341241386"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/268608902/answer/341241386">考私人飞行执照是怎样一种体验？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>12</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">12</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/wang-vinzent" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-vinzent'>Vinzent</a>，<span title="《舒克日记》专栏作家/FAA私照飞行员/走过7大洲80国/" class="bio">《舒克日记》专栏作家/FAA私照飞行员/走过7大洲80国/</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="Vinzent" data-entry-url="/question/268608902/answer/341241386"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">只有在美国学习和考试的经历，所以……只能比较片面的回答。考这个执照的具体过程有很多答案都写的比较清楚了，首先不是美国籍的人都需要进行TSA的背景调查，之后才能开始学习飞行。之后就是体检，飞行训练和地面课程。地面课程上到一定程度就要参加笔试，…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/268608902/answer/341241386">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="12"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/Bat006" data-hovercard='p$t$Bat006'>小福小腻小福腻</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/liang-ge-er" data-hovercard='p$t$liang-ge-er'>梁哥儿2333</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/wang-zhi-yang-47-92" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-zhi-yang-47-92'>Std.Winters</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>只有在美国学习和考试的经历，所以……只能比较片面的回答。</p><p>考这个执照的具体过程有很多答案都写的比较清楚了，首先不是美国籍的人都需要进行TSA的背景调查，之后才能开始学习飞行。之后就是体检，飞行训练和地面课程。地面课程上到一定程度就要参加笔试，通过之后继续飞行训练和地面课程。等飞行小时数达到之后，就可以申请最后的考试，包括口试和飞行技能测试。通过了，考官会给你签发一张纸质的执照，有效期120天，在这段日子当中FAA会制作你的永久执照，并给你寄送到你要的地址。</p><p>要说体验，真的是从头到尾的幸福感，偶尔穿插着挫败感。毕竟有语言上的问题，很多时候需要拼时间去死记硬背一些东西（而且知识点确实很多）。但因为是自己的梦想，还是能坚持下来的。总体说是一个一生难忘的体验。</p><p></p></script><a class="time" href="/question/268608902/answer/341241386">2018-03-14</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>12</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="21877066"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">5 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone">