swer-id" content="91816978"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="339655576"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/31763792/answer/339655576">如何从零开始成为一个飞行员？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>39</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">39</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/wang-vinzent" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-vinzent'>Vinzent</a>，<span title="《舒克日记》专栏作家/FAA私照飞行员/走过7大洲80国/" class="bio">《舒克日记》专栏作家/FAA私照飞行员/走过7大洲80国/</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="Vinzent" data-entry-url="/question/31763792/answer/339655576"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">各位大神 <a class="member_mention" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/272d7473145fe195295db3a015c262f6" data-hash="272d7473145fe195295db3a015c262f6" data-hovercard="p$b$272d7473145fe195295db3a015c262f6">@车尔尼雷夫司机</a> <a class="member_mention" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7" data-hash="5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7" data-hovercard="p$b$5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7">@书放</a> 都回答了在中国成为民航飞行员的步骤，我想就个人经历说一下，如果你成为不了中国民航的飞行员，还是有可能成为飞行员的。我是因为视力不过关，而且有纹身。我在知乎写了本书，叫玩点不一样：30天学会开飞机，为了配合这次…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/31763792/answer/339655576">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="39"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/cao-jia-wei-28-19" data-hovercard='p$t$cao-jia-wei-28-19'>ZSPD17LPIK11X</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/hhhhhhh-2-1" data-hovercard='p$t$hhhhhhh-2-1'>hhhhhhh</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/zhao-ming-hao-50-49" data-hovercard='p$t$zhao-ming-hao-50-49'>赵明浩</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>各位大神 <a class="member_mention" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/272d7473145fe195295db3a015c262f6" data-hash="272d7473145fe195295db3a015c262f6" data-hovercard="p$b$272d7473145fe195295db3a015c262f6">@车尔尼雷夫司机</a> <a class="member_mention" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7" data-hash="5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7" data-hovercard="p$b$5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7">@书放</a> 都回答了在中国成为民航飞行员的步骤，我想就个人经历说一下，如果你成为不了中国民航的飞行员，还是有可能成为飞行员的。</p><p>我是因为视力不过关，而且有纹身。</p><p>我在知乎写了本书，叫玩点不一样：30天学会开飞机，为了配合这次知乎圆桌<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/roundtable/feixingyuan" class="internal">成为飞行员</a>，我决定从今天（2018年3月12日）到本周三晚上12点之前，所有想看这本书的人可以知乎私信我，我送你。知乎并没有给我免费送书的份额，我自己出钱，但我希望你看完之后这本书能在你心里埋下一颗种子，希望早晚有一天能实现这个不太简单却又不太困难的梦想。</p><p>连接在此：<a href="https://www.zhihu.com/pub/book/119557285" class="internal">玩点不一样：30 天学会开飞机</a></p><p>民航的飞行员要求确实高，因为承载着很多的责任。就好像开大公共汽车一样，大公共汽车的司机一定是要求更严格。但，如果你真的想成为飞行员，而由于各种原因又当不了民航飞行员，那就当个普通的私照飞行员也好。就像开私家车和大公共汽车一样的对比，私家车（私照飞行员）其实更自由，想去哪就能去哪，想停在哪里就停在哪里，什么路线时间自己说了算，相对来说自由很多。</p><p>私照飞行员的执照，是一个license to learn。它会为你打开飞行的大门。之后的挑战、知识、经验会越来越多，这是一个新世界。</p><p>要玩就得这么玩</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956496624583753728" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-02e6c8b0f4ced81d0a986b2b883a08b1_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956496624583753728">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-02e6c8b0f4ced81d0a986b2b883a08b1_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956496624583753728</span>              </span>            </a><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956497827950579712" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-ae5e1a2d889b44c65b6c908939c24f3a_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956497827950579712">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-ae5e1a2d889b44c65b6c908939c24f3a_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956497827950579712</span>              </span>            </a><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956502939502645248" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-90af1830b02fe4b4f9946a51644fb0ec_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956502939502645248">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-90af1830b02fe4b4f9946a51644fb0ec_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956502939502645248</span>              </span>            </a><p>网侵删</p><p>更多的内容，敬请关注专栏《舒克日记》。<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/aviator" class="internal">舒克日记</a></p></script><a class="time" href="/question/31763792/answer/339655576">2018-03-12</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>39</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id=