ata-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-91842839"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/30424714/answer/339797181"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="4352260"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="30424714"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="91842839"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="339797181"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/30424714/answer/339797181">飞行员在学飞过程中都有过哪些难忘的经历？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>28</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">28</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/wang-vinzent" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-vinzent'>Vinzent</a>，<span title="《舒克日记》专栏作家/FAA私照飞行员/走过7大洲80国/" class="bio">《舒克日记》专栏作家/FAA私照飞行员/走过7大洲80国/</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="Vinzent" data-entry-url="/question/30424714/answer/339797181"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">跟别的大神不一样的是，我因为参加的是普通航校，不是民航在国外的合同航校，所以我的航校气氛相对轻松。教员对我是像朋友一样，所以学习也都是按部就班的学，没有什么特别难的地方，当然，我的技术也属于100分满分能打60分的技术。但是确实有一些对自己来…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/30424714/answer/339797181">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="28"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/maybejustyou" data-hovercard='p$t$maybejustyou'>maybe</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/cao-jia-wei-28-19" data-hovercard='p$t$cao-jia-wei-28-19'>ZSPD17LPIK11X</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/Bat006" data-hovercard='p$t$Bat006'>小福小腻小福腻</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>跟别的大神不一样的是，我因为参加的是普通航校，不是民航在国外的合同航校，所以我的航校气氛相对轻松。教员对我是像朋友一样，所以学习也都是按部就班的学，没有什么特别难的地方，当然，我的技术也属于100分满分能打60分的技术。</p><p>但是确实有一些对自己来说比较难忘的经历。</p><p>第一次Preflight的时候检查油，发现有水，虽然不多。</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956550807944990720" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-51851296799ecda3fca80630943460e1_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956550807944990720">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-51851296799ecda3fca80630943460e1_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956550807944990720</span>              </span>            </a><p>准备起飞的时候跑道附近有个乌龟 <a class="member_mention" href="//www.zhihu.com/people/5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7" data-hash="5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7" data-hovercard="p$b$5e7780fcbfbca5723b34d7122c3048b7">@书放</a> </p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/956551873935683584" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="true" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-6bd26759f64f66c8f87335019f557557_b.jpg" data-lens-id="956551873935683584">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-6bd26759f64f66c8f87335019f557557_b.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/956551873935683584</span>              </span>            </a><p>还有考过的时候……</p><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?